article_title: Obamacare's 'Accountable Care' Experiment Is All Hype, No Substance

article_metadata.description: There's nothing innovative about the "Accountable Care" model. It has, at best, generated negligible savings. And it has set the stage for outright rationing of senior medical care.
article_metadata.author: Sally Pipes
